<problem id="fs-idm357806160">
<para id="fs-idm343658752"><link class="lo-reference" document="m68077"/>Assume you are the manager of a local <emphasis class="colored-text">Starbucks</emphasis>. What factors do you feel would be relevant to hiring workers (including pay), assuming <emphasis class="colored-text">Starbucks</emphasis> is a centralized organization?</para>
</problem>
</exercise>
