<glossary>
<definition id="fs-idm346301168">
<term>segment</term>
<meaning id="fs-idm346300528">portion of the business that management believes has sufficient similarities in product lines, geographic locations, or customers to warrant reporting that portion of the company as a distinct part of the entire company</meaning>
</definition>
<definition id="fs-idm346300016">
<term>organizational chart</term>
<meaning id="fs-idm346299376">graphical representations illustrating the authority for decision-making and oversight throughout an organization</meaning>
</definition>
</glossary>
